{"tid":497422,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係我疑心重定的士錶真係跳得好快","createTime":"2017-12-12T17:40:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T19:11:32.000Z","uid":152000,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bfbd4f1966dd9e682d4c84945be73b3619d3dde8","tid":497422,"uid":152000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T17:40:33.000Z","msg":"小弟啱先由荃灣路德圍上的士反葵芳。<br />\n咁正常出反大馬路行就穿得到葵芳，司機遍遍要兜路兜到上大窩口我都算喇唔講太多因為太急住反歸喇。<br />\n但最唔明嘅係架的士上咗半條斜路就跳三下錶？我當堂眼都凸哂同司機講咗句個錶跳得咁勁嘅好似，但司機選擇無視。<br />\n半條斜路都算，成條斜路計真係跳我6次錶，每下等紅綠燈又跳，我望住個錶愈跳得開心我就愈緊張。<br />\n當司機穿過葵涌邨喇終於落到新葵花園我即刻嗌落，佢仲喺度下下聲唔想開門咁款，嗰時隻錶已經跳到成$5x，自問坐咁近距離跳到咁勁真係第一次見識到。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知係我疑心重定其實係正常呢.."},{"pid":"779f65d797d665c688a338839ec866e485f49245","tid":497422,"uid":1813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T17:44:41.000Z","msg":"反你老母"},{"pid":"0fcd9bc0e5a62f642048d342cfa4c146a74626b9","tid":497422,"uid":1696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T18:04:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/020402_767c2cac353f27cb6d3aa26144d3ea52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F020402_767c2cac353f27cb6d3aa26144d3ea52.jpg&h=baf96148&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n兜完路差唔多啦"},{"pid":"5b0f67d0087039826e99b47dfc1445abc71e2165","tid":497422,"uid":57962,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T18:14:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2df17c3ee32612b5bf378a9c8e935e405d05855e","tid":497422,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T18:44:50.000Z","msg":"落車問佢拎張收據囉 睇下行左幾遠幾耐"},{"pid":"a0b3a55f43bc07e9b260f19f1bc4610722a57799","tid":497422,"uid":93069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T18:45:46.000Z","msg":"仲益班dc dog 搭uber la人地態度又好 又坐得舒服<br />\n重點係一定唔會話唔識路拒載"},{"pid":"0cc7e1daf6c7e80a7a9616a3dc45cc6aa97d7b89","tid":497422,"uid":147205,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T18:58:57.000Z","msg":"痴撚線...窮西就下次早啲搭交通工具返屋企啦<br />\n我係的士佬都選擇唔理9你啦問埋啲on9問題<br />\n唔通答你: 哈哈，係呀，個錶佢好撚跳得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左行車距離，仲有行車時間都會影響跳錶<br />\n你覺得個的士佬會搞咁多野去呃你幾廿蚊？<br />\n要呃錢直接去劏客唔好？"},{"pid":"50504df025cb43f3c6e6016f2951803c4e832c8e","tid":497422,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T19:11:32.000Z","msg":"窮西真係好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}